  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a hot pot vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped bell pepper and cook until tender, about 4 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped tomato and cook until the vegetables are tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Pour in the cranberry juice and stir to combine.",
    "Add the shredded akawi cheese and stir until melted and well combined.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley if desired."
